{"tid":1064883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】林鄭在任送了多少個億給大地產商?","createTime":"2019-03-17T00:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T04:12:15.000Z","uid":138409,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bff1e82e6cedbd3a2d20f970e293689eacd3a0a8","tid":1064883,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:54:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">tl;dr</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFdUrZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFdUrZk.jpg&h=18454d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2225706684192059/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2Fphotos%2Fa.326590167437063%2F2225706684192059%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=85d7b80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/photos/a.326590167437063/2225706684192059/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n由地產商選出的林鄭月娥，究竟在任有沒有在土地政策回禮? 箇中交易我們不得而知，但近日林鄭就已將香港天水一色的豐樂圍濕地偷步批出許可，在任近兩年又有沒有在土地發展大計瘋狂密密送?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 豐樂圍濕地偷雞送長實 (81公頃)：</span><br />\n<br />\n長實一直囤積在<span style=\"color: gold;\">受國際公約保護的濕地</span>範圍，企圖興建19棟豪宅近2,000個單位。近日就在<span style=\"color: gold;\">未符合規劃許可</span>條件下(找環團合作保育)，屋宇署仍格外批出了圖則，當中涉及<span style=\"color: gold;\">過百億</span>潛在土地利益。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 300億公帑貼新世界建啟德體育城 (28公頃)：</span><br />\n<br />\n近月林鄭又將啟德體育城整塊土地批予新世界地產，交易極度闊綽，不僅<span style=\"color: gold;\">318億建築費由政府包底，而且無條件再送20年專營權</span>，而將來政府只收當中3%收益，世界上還那裡可找到一個比這個更筍的發展計劃?<br />\n<br />\n計劃批出嘅同時更提議將香港大球場座位大規模減少，讓將來新世界營運的啟德體育城搖身一變成香港唯一大型戶外場館，<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫地產商投資消除競爭建立壟斷</span>，唔惦都攪到包賺。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 超級航天城新世界又中 (57公頃)：</span><br />\n<br />\n機場 有<span style=\"color: gold;\">57公頃</span>土地，又不經不覺長期以直送予新世界興建及營運的方式獨得，這個「超級航天城」發展規模 (總建築樓面面積達300萬平方呎)，<span style=\"color: gold;\">將會比香港最大的商場海港城還要巨大</span>。<br />\n<br />\n這場交易的結果，是直至2066年，政府與新世界的收益分帳是20%: 80%。天啊，世界上為何還有這樣好的良心大地主?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. 新鴻基十四鄉豪宅要加倍嗎? 來吧。(76.4公頃)</span><br />\n<br />\n去年新鴻基獲批了76.4公頃十四鄉豪宅補地價，面積足足約<span style=\"color: red;\">4個維園</span>，都在林鄭任內藉「增加土地供應」之名又送地產發展利益的傑作。批出後，還准許修改建屋數目由5,000個激增至<span style=\"color: gold;\">9,500間豪宅</span>，經常聲稱「土地共享」，<span style=\"color: gold;\">這裡未來一間可負擔房屋都找不到啊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5. 灣仔會展擴建整定官地又批新世界</span><br />\n<br />\n事源1985年貿發局曾與新世界立下一條不平等壟斷條款 (「無競爭權」條款)，指未來40年會展擴建都只能批予新世界營運。今屆林鄭在施政報告大興土木大舉，計劃大舉搬走三幢政府大樓(稅務大樓、入境事務處和灣仔政府大廈)，最終就很可能是<span style=\"color: gold;\">為了騰出政府土地送予新世界擴建會展</span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府在任短短不足兩年，一直聲稱土地不足，又<span style=\"color: gold;\">大撒幣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />200億買60間鋪，另一邊廂則將上幾百公頃市區靚地一塊一塊特惠送給大地產商，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實每年政府平均撥給公營房屋的土地都只是大約20公頃而已。</span></span>你們星斗市民癩蝦蟆就想吃天鵝肉? 知道世界上有地產霸權這回事嗎?"},{"pid":"258daf8a41df644097e259f323f07a414e25287e","tid":1064883,"uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"⚔️ 結束土地壟斷 請支持民間土地研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fresearch-category%2Fland-supply%2F&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=19dfafce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/research-category/land-supply/</a><br />\n💪 了解更多: <a href=\"http://liber-research.com/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fabout-us&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=3e9fee95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://liber-research.com/about-us</a>"},{"pid":"a9a0ea2853073a1e41122bb29b0e647621739dbf","tid":1064883,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T00:57:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c12eedf073e6d64377edc829c02ac8ab2de455c3","tid":1064883,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"腥港十個字就總結哂<br />\n<br />\n官商鄉黑自由勾結市場"},{"pid":"00ef4b4dd266846c20ed1fa8f6c7495139b66221","tid":1064883,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb3ac51d7db0e908422adf15c19d18d1a4a09400","tid":1064883,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"339102495a72e90a1045358affe3f6d5aa6480c9","tid":1064883,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c12eedf073e6d64377edc829c02ac8ab2de455c3","tid":1064883,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:08:06.000Z","msg":"腥港十個字就總結哂<br />\n<br />\n官商鄉黑自由勾結市場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:23:13.000Z","msg":"共產黨先係最大利益者"},{"pid":"76d1fa5d845847a799792e0ae878e434eec6ebb2","tid":1064883,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T01:36:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"69f14699bf0cc61d7a53822a947f273457677faa","tid":1064883,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28091536bb71580449559903c80e1b1839be635d","tid":1064883,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"Icac正垃圾"},{"pid":"3e61c0892aaad8638c8bb358fe6ebce4d8b2b50d","tid":1064883,"uid":40779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講漏咗<br />\n<br />\n公屋果20公頃係俾新移民<br />\n香港人乜都冇呀"},{"pid":"85a3f2c8379ddc567f8a2510ace6420b421d3fee","tid":1064883,"uid":182330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb53f699a0c94d38b9bbcfca7190aaf06d3ece67","tid":1064883,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"香港嘅所謂民主只不過係貴族議會制<br />\n賤民安份守己就得架啦，其他野唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0c61df2c8ea7f868f742bd6aef8866dee4b823","tid":1064883,"uid":208932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"土地「共」享"},{"pid":"35a394c2bceb8054c1165a6670675cec986be331","tid":1064883,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2285dde031ba653ac61e56aa17730b0fea4cc262","tid":1064883,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab32fc25921c6278a0ff4b8552200e64c0eca5a","tid":1064883,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"水管屋就一大堆柒頭話人地為反而反<br />\n<br />\n你老到智障又唔喺度留言屌淋病 ?  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n含撚啦"},{"pid":"5edb7efeeaa5608ba6f621196ce54a171a5f5a4a","tid":1064883,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:04:54.000Z","msg":"多少「個」億？<br />\n<br />\n億就億，個你老母呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c840de978dc19acd1fa6416552fd491d6ca04","tid":1064883,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"貪污"}]}